@startuml 03-user-logout
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title User Logout

actor User
participant "AppShell\n(Angular)" as SPA
participant "POST /api/auth/logout" as API
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "revoked_tokens" as DB

User -> SPA: tap Log out
SPA -> API: POST /api/auth/logout\n(cookie or Bearer)
API -> CTX: INSERT revoked (jti, expiresAt)
CTX -> DB: INSERT
DB --> CTX: ok
API --> SPA: 204\nSet-Cookie: rq_sid=; Max-Age=0
SPA -> SPA: clear session signal
SPA --> User: redirect /login

... later ...
SPA -> API: GET /api/contacts\nwith stale token
API -> CTX: is jti revoked?
CTX -> DB: SELECT
DB --> CTX: found
CTX --> API: revoked
API --> SPA: 401 Unauthorized
SPA --> User: force re-login

@enduml
